eam are focused on growing ncr’s strategic solutions in omnichannel software including ncr’s omnichannel platform channel transformation and digital enablement solutions read more edward gallagher svp general counsel and secretary executive officer edward gallagher is the senior vice president general counsel and secretary of ncr corporation since joining ncr in  ed has served in a number of leadership positions including head of the company’s litigation  employment law group chief counsel for the systemedia division and chief counsel of the year  group read more ruth fornell svp global professional services ruth fornell is senior vice president of global professional services for ncr corporation in this role she leads a team of  professionals and is responsible for professional services consultants and delivering technical and business consulting services worldwide read more j robert ciminera evp hardware product operations executive officer as executive vice president of hardware product operations for ncr corporation bob ciminera is responsible for ncr’s financial retail and hospitality product portfolios this includes engineering product life cycle management material supply chain manufacturing customer fulfillment and reverse logistics as well as managing b of other corporate spend in this capacity he is responsible for driving more than m in cost improvement per year while ensuring product innovation product quality on time customer delivery and high working capital efficiency read more eli rosner chief technology officer  head of product management eli rosner is chief technology officer cto  head of product management for ncr corporation in this role he is accountable for the company’s strategy formulation development and crossfunctional delivery of ncr’s software portfolio rosner also participates in the ncr leadership team led by ncr’s president ceo and chairman bill nuti read more william bill t vancuren svp  chief information officer bill vancuren is senior vice president and chief information officer for ncr corporation in his role bill is responsible for the full strategic it portfolio global networks and processing services for both internal and external customer managed services as well as all workgroup collaborative and mobile computing he also oversees information security and compliancy as well as ncr’s saas datacenter strategy and operations read more news ncr announces second quarter  results ncr corporation nyse ncr reported financial results today for the three months ended june   read more ncr corporation we had an incredible time volunteering with the atlantafalcons at the bellwood boys  girls club today ncrlife httpstcoahrpzgndi blog how authentic can aid the transition to psd and open apis the second iteration of the eus payment services directive psd is on the horizon due to come into full effect for all eu member states by january  this is a major legislative change whose repercussions will be felt throughout the financial services industry read more did you know over  of the worlds  million atms are ncr machines united continental holdings names william r nuti to board of directors united continental holdings names william r nuti to board of directors dec    et from united airlines united airlines logo prnewsfotounited airlines     facebook twitter pinterest united airlines logo prnewsfotounited airlines chicago dec   prnewswire  united continental holdings nyse ual today announced that william bill nuti is joining its board of directors effective today nuti is chairman ceo and president of ncr corporation the global leader in consumer transaction technologies since his arrival at ncr in  nuti has orchestrated a highly successful reinvention of the global technology company prior to joining ncr nuti served as president and ceo of symbol technologies inc nuti joined symbol from cisco systems inc where he served in the dual role of senior vice president of the companys worldwide service provider operations and senior vice president of us theater operations bill is a great addition to our board of directors said ual chairman president and ceo jeff smisek bill has unique experience helping businesses connect with their customers using technology and he will be a tremendous asset as we expand our online mobile and customer selfservice options at united technology is rapidly transforming how consumers connect interact and transact with business said nuti i look forward to joining the united board as the company continues to explore new ways of delivering an omnichannel experience to consumers nuti is a member of the georgia institute of technology advisory board and a long island university trustee he holds a bachelors degree in finance and economics from long island university about united united airlines and united express operate an average of more than  flights a day to more than  airports across six continents in  united and united express carried more passenger traffic than any other airline in the world and operated nearly two million flights carrying  million customers united is investing in upgrading its onboard products and now offers more flatbed seats in its premium cabins and more extralegroom economyclass seating than any airline in north america in  united became the first usbased international carrier to offer satellitebased wifi on longhaul overseas routes the airline also features directv® on more than  aircraft offering customers more live television access than any other airline in the world united operates nearly  mainline aircraft and has made largescale investments in its fleet in  united continues to modernize its fleet by taking delivery of more than two dozen new boeing aircraft the company will have launched  new international and  new domestic routes including the addition of seven new cities to its network by the end of  business traveler magazine awarded united best airline for north american travel for  and readers of global traveler magazine have voted uniteds mileageplus program the best frequent flyer program for nine consecutive years according to the th annual switchfly reward seat availability survey published by ideaworkscompany in may  united has the most saverstyle awardseat availability among the largest us global airlines air transport world named united as the ecoaviation airline of the year gold winner in  united is a founding member of star alliance which provides service to  countries via  member airlines more than  united employees reside in every us state and in countries around the world for more information visit unitedcom or follow united on twitter and facebook the common stock of uniteds parent united continental holdings inc is traded on the nyse under the symbol ual logo httpphotosprnewswirecomprnhmmlogo source united airlines related links httpwwwunitedcom httpirunitedcom view table fullscreen view table fullscreen journalists and bloggers the news you need when you need it join pr newswire for journalists to access all of the free services designated to make your job easier in need of subject matter experts for your story submit a free profnet request and find the sources you need learn more dec    et preview greg hart to become chief operations officer of united airlines dec    et preview united airlines completes redesign of ps premium service fleet my news release contains wide tables view fullscreen read more jul    et united airlines names terri fariello head of government affairs jul    et united airlines reports secondquarter  performance jul    et united reports june  operational performance looking to send a news release with pr newswire take advantage of the worlds leading distribution platform sign up to get started request more information have an account log in search searching for your content advanced search nuti william  insider stock trading  openinsider sector all sectors group by sector aerospace agriculture automobile building business services chemi